Package com.enttribe.superapp.service.generic

Class AbstractService<T>

java.lang.Object
com.enttribe.superapp.service.generic.AbstractService<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type parameter representing the entity that this service manages.
All Implemented Interfaces:
GenericService<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
HostingDetailsServiceImpl, MiniappBuildDetailsServiceImpl, MiniappDetailsServiceImpl
public abstract class AbstractService<T> extends Object implements GenericService<T>
The AbstractService class is an abstract implementation of the GenericService interface. This class provides a base implementation for common service functionalities.
